musculacion.name: Musculacionee
musculacion.description: Musculacion is a comprehensive fitness program designed to enhance strength, endurance, and overall physical health. It includes a variety of exercises targeting different muscle groups, ensuring a balanced workout routine.

musculacion.name: Musculacion Avanzada
musculacion.description: Musculacion Avanzada is an advanced fitness program for experienced individuals looking to push their limits. It includes high-intensity workouts and specialized training techniques.

musculacion.name: Musculacion para Principiantes
musculacion.description: Musculacion para Principiantes is designed for those new to fitness. It focuses on basic exercises and proper form to build a solid foundation.

musculacion.name: Musculacion Funcional
musculacion.description: Musculacion Funcional combines traditional strength training with functional movements to improve overall fitness and daily performance.

crossfit.name: Crossfit
crossfit.description: Crossfit is a high-intensity fitness program that combines elements of cardio, weightlifting, and functional movements. It is designed to improve overall fitness and athletic performance.

crossfit.name: Crossfit Avanzado
crossfit.description: Crossfit Avanzado is for experienced athletes looking to take their training to the next level. It includes advanced techniques and high-intensity workouts.
